parameters: Carelessly wandering through the middle of the hallway...\.\.
You were unable to get out of harm's way in time.\.\.
Trampled into a unrecognizeable smear by a single stray footfall;
no one will ever conceive you were anything more than an insect.
\n<Female Teacher>I thought I saw a bug on the floor...
Mistaken for a bug by one of the school's teachers on her way
to her next class, she decided to quickly eradicate you
beneath her heels rather than waste any time examining you closer.
incredible force of her descending foot, you now existed as
nothing more than a minute stain on the bottom of her shoe.\.\.
One which would be gradually wiped away as the teacher merely went about her schedule.
